<title type="html"><![CDATA[7/15 (Thu.) Silver linings of Covid (host: Rock)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=523&amp;p=546#p546"><![CDATA[
<span style="font-size: 130%; line-height: normal"><span style="color: #800000"><span style="font-weight: bold">7/15 (Thu.) Silver linings of Covid (host: Rock)</span></span></span>  (under construction)<br /><br />Hi, guys, long time no see.  My pleasure to host in Royal again.  I'd like to invite you guys to talk about Covid, but only on the positive side.  There is  too much bad news already.  This time, let's stick to the good.<br /><br />The lockdown is coming to the end, and we can hopefully live like what we did before.  Covid is very bad, but even the worst storm has its silver lining.  What good things happened in the world thanks to this pandemic?  What things in your life that are actually good because of Covid?  <br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.predictiveindex.com/blog/covid-19-silver-linings/">https://www.predictiveindex.com/blog/co ... r-linings/</a><!-- m --><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.quora.com/What-are-some-silver-linings-to-the-global-COVID-19-outbreak">https://www.quora.com/What-are-some-sil ... 9-outbreak</a><!-- m --><br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Questions<br />Session One<br />1. Many people work from home because of Covid; some people actually enjoy it.  What are the good and fun things of WFH?<br />2. Students learn from home in Covid lockdown.  What's good about LFH?  What are the things of LFH that are better than real school? <br />3. What positive things do you have because of Covid 19?<br /><br />Session Two<br />4. What positive things happened in the world thanks to Covid?<br />5. What are the worst things happened in Covid times?  How can people handle them and find a silver linings of them?<br />6. What lessons can human beings learn from Covid?　</span><br /><br />-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br /><br />Place: Zoom Meeting<br />Agenda:<br />07:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks<br />07:05-7:40 pm Session 1 Group Discussion<br />07:40-8:00 pm Presentation (At least two members of each table are invited, 2 mins / each member)<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:40 pm Session 2 discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Presentation<br /><br />Let's join the Zoom meeting this Thursday at 07:00 pm<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ... 09#success<br /><br />會議 ID:929 8726 6213<br />密碼:112233<br /><br />------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br /><br /><br />P.S.<br />1.因疫情關係，聚會方式改為線上遠距。<br />2.參加三次後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />3.請帶著開放與熱情來參加自由的全英文會話聚會~<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=566">rock1101</a> — Fri Jul 09, 2021 1:10 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
